basic functionality:
- player selects scene: key, mode, 7ths vs triads, which diatonic chords, if/which secondary dominants, if/which substitute dominants, 
- random key selected, tonic played —> number keys now play diatonic triads + modifiers for secondary/sub —> random chord within scene is played
- buttons: repeat tonic, repeat chord, arpegiate chord, display answer,  
- prefs: numberkeys on/off, arpegiate always, play chord during answer reveal, gen MIDI sound select, answer root/fullchord toggle

advanced:
- octave select
- arpeggiate 
- inversions 
- voiceleading

